{
  "texts": [
    "Another significant aspect is the significance of explainable AI in addressing class imbalance, especially in activity detection tasks.",
    "Incorporating explainability into prediction models would provide insights into decision-making processes, hence increasing transparency and usability for healthcare professionals and assistive technology users.",
    "Future research will investigate the integration of explainability frameworks with advanced optimization methods to guarantee fair and interpretable results.",
    "Additionally, in future work, further tuning of the IYSGA parameters will be investigated for better results.To design an innovative mechanism named AH-CNN-LSTM (Adaptive Hybrid Convolution Neural Network) with a Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) to analyze the EEG (electroencephalogram)/EMG signals, which is the fusion of CNN and LSTM, to provide better suggestions to the caretakers more accurately without any error.",
    "• A new human motion intention detection model named AH-CNN-Res-LSTM (AH-CNN Residual Network-LSTM) with sensor data is constructed by merging the Res-LSTM and CNN techniques to resolve flexibility by providing precise human motion prediction outcomes."
  ]
}